@post_election
on-arrival: {!
// set congress proportion to votes
Q.spd_r = Q.spd_votes;
Q.cdu_r = Q.z_votes;
Q.sapd_r = Q.kpd_votes;
Q.aspd_r = Q.ddp_votes;
Q.lvp_r = Q.dvp_votes;
Q.dkp_r = Q.dnvp_votes;
Q.ndpd_r = Q.nsdap_votes;
Q.other_r = Q.other_votes;

// The largest party can only be the NSDAP or the SPD.
Q.largest_party = 'SPD';
if (Q.nsdap_r >= Q.spd_r && Q.nsdap_r >= Q.kpd_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'NSDAP';
}
if (Q.kpd_r >= Q.spd_r && Q.kpd_r >= Q.nsdap_r) {
    Q.largest_party = 'KPD';
}

// coalitions
Q.weimar_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.lvp_r + Q.cdu_r - 3;
Q.grand_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.aspd_r + Q.cdu_r + Q.lvp_r;
Q.bourgeois_coalition = Q.aspd_r + Q.cdu_r + Q.lvp_r + Q.other_r;
Q.center_right_coalition = Q.cdu_r + Q.lvp_r + Q.other_r + Q.dkp_r;
Q.right_coalition = Q.lvp_r + Q.other_r + Q.dkp_r;
Q.far_right_coalition = Q.dkp_r + Q.ndpd_r;
Q.left_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.sapd_r;
// this is an absurd concept lol
Q.united_front_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.sapd_r + Q.cdu_r + Q.aspd_r - 3;
Q.anti_democratic_coalition = Q.sapd_r + Q.ndpd_r;
// aka everyone except nazi, kpd, dnvp
Q.neo_weimar_coalition = Q.spd_r + Q.aspd_r + Q.cdu_r + Q.lvp_r + Q.other_r;
!}

The electoral system is essentially proportional, with the proportion of Reichstag seats roughly equal to the proportion of votes.
 
**Election results:**

# 1928: 30, 1930: 25, 1932: 22
SPD: [+ spd_r +]

# 1928: 15, 1930: 15, 1932: 
CDU + BVP: [+ cdu_r +]

# 1928: 10, 1930: 13
SAPD: [+ sapd_r +]

# 1928: 5, 1930: 4 (as DstP)
ASPD: [+ aspd_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 5
LVP: [+ lvp_r +]

# 1928: 14, 1930: 7
DkP: [+ dkp_r +]

# 1928: 3, 1930: 18
NDPD: [+ ndpd_r +]

# 1928: 9, 1930: 10
Other: [+ other_r +]

**Potential coalitions:**

Weimar Coalition (SPD + CDU + LVP): [+ weimar_coalition +]

Grand Coalition (SPD + ASPD + CDU + BVP + LVP): [+ grand_coalition +]

Bourgeois Coalition (ASPD + CDU + BVP + LVP + Others): [+ bourgeois_coalition +]

Right-wing Coalition (BVP + LVP + Others + DkP): [+ right_coalition +]

